        <div class="tc-bar-wrapper">
          <div id="tc-bar-actual-loss" class="tc-bar" style="background: #EA2D2E; width: 0%; min-width: 4px;"></div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="tc-insight tc-insight-red">
        <strong>Insight:</strong> To keep ₦71.06 trillion in customer deposits secure, Access, GTCO, and UBA collectively spent roughly <strong>131 times more</strong> on defense systems than what they actually lost to cybercriminals.
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

