    <h3 class="tc-header-title">The ARPU Gap: Value vs. Velocity</h3>
    <p style="font-weight: 400; font-size: 1rem; color: #4A5568; margin: 0; line-height: 1.6;">Francophone Africa still extracts the most revenue per user, but Nigeria&#8217;s recent 50% tariff hike has triggered explosive year-over-year growth.</p>
